parameters.name: AcceptLanguage
parameters.description:
The language of the response. Valid values:

*   zh: Chinese
*   en: English

parameters.name: ConnectType
parameters.description:
The network type. Valid values:

*   slb
*   eni

parameters.name: MseVersion
parameters.description:
The edition of the MSE instance that you want to purchase.

*   mse_pro: Professional Edition
*   mse_dev: Developer Edition

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The ID of the region in which the instance resides. The region is supported by Microservices Engine (MSE).
